channel.title: Join The Joeocity Project
channel.description:
The joeocity project is the project to create the ultimate moparscape server. Once this server is designed it will be hosted on a vps payed for by me. I am looking for a group of 5 people to design it. If needed more people will be accepted. The only requirment for this project is to know how to design a mopar server. To Join please email me with your contact details and I will get back to you. Please wait until tommorow for a full post on my website.
Joeocityproject.com is the place to find out about the project.
The Mopar server domain will be joeocity.com . Joeocityproject.com is still under construction.
Once we get enough people we will start the development.
My email: joe@joeocityproject.com My aim screename: joeocity my gtalk name: joeocity
That is all for now. Please be paitent.
Joe, Head and Owner of The Joeocity project
